OL,3,CMan arrested and charged following
OL,4,Ccrash in Dumfries
OL,6,FA 71-year-old man has been arrested
OL,7,Fand charged in connection with a crash
OL,8,Fin Dumfries which injured three
OL,9,Fchildren.
OL,11,FThe incident was reported around
OL,12,F3.15pm on Monday, October 13 2025.
OL,14,FThe children, aged eight months, 14
OL,15,Fmonths and 18-months-old, were taken
OL,16,Fto Dumfries and Galloway Royal
OL,17,FInfirmary, before being transferred to
OL,18,Fthe Royal Children's Hospital in
OL,19,FGlasgow for treatment to serious
OL,20,Finjuries.
