OL,3,CMan arrested and charged following
OL,4,Ccrash in Dumfries
OL,6,FThe 18-year-old woman who was pushing
OL,7,Fa pram was also taken to the hospital
OL,8,Ffor treatment.
OL,10,FAll involved were later discharged.
OL,12,FThe man has been reported to the
OL,13,FProcurator Fiscal.
